{"tid":481390,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人成日都會去貓CAFE?","createTime":"2017-11-27T06:40:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-05T16:49:56.000Z","uid":140094,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"9f846941c5856fd5c6ab80b29be2b207c3640b5d","tid":481390,"uid":140094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T06:40:46.000Z","msg":"做緊份有關貓CAFE既功課 想了解下成日都會去貓CAFE既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb852844a97e1cb2a2371283855f5c1486f27219","tid":481390,"uid":156326,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T06:43:19.000Z","msg":"去間cafe訪問啲人咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b742b72b5e02841a55ab4ac233ae2314989882f9","tid":481390,"uid":140094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T06:49:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去間cafe訪問啲人咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n之後會去 但我驚嚇走人地D客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd861b525ad3d8e3b27aa90f59bc9dd61ff82ffe","tid":481390,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T06:51:21.000Z","msg":"點define 成日?"},{"pid":"d21caa42ee0af73431d91a22fe58018180ecf9fd","tid":481390,"uid":140094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T06:55:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點define 成日?</blockquote><br />\n起碼一個月一次或者每隔一段時間都會去 姐係有去貓cafe呢個習慣既人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aab0e61e47cef1e115bf3515bf70f577c7c388e7","tid":481390,"uid":64318,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T06:59:05.000Z","msg":"當你養左貓就覺得開呢d鋪既人好撚9"},{"pid":"25eccd2b9c4f52a90adeb02a2d2283a317a9a0bd","tid":481390,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T07:00:27.000Z","msg":"我"},{"pid":"2b90c29cfaa60b3bb33b6a2e65505291db0fe354","tid":481390,"uid":151630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T07:04:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當你養左貓就覺得開呢d鋪既人好撚9</blockquote><br />\n同意"},{"pid":"465eba1608f3e50b167aeb8695f696ea8320630f","tid":481390,"uid":50779,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T07:09:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1d666b5d0f2f02ff0eaa048ff19695bb6999982b","tid":481390,"uid":104658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T07:14:36.000Z","msg":"新界有無邊幾間仲未執  好推介<br />\n<br />\n上網睇好似執哂 最近都係要出旺角"},{"pid":"2f35bd37c4ec6a50497da429a382a9d82b47ac8c","tid":481390,"uid":11774,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T10:34:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>新界有無邊幾間仲未執  好推介<br />\n<br />\n上網睇好似執哂 最近都係要出旺角</blockquote><br />\n就係多得你哋呢班仆街幫襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n先會有人攞貓嚟做生意 根本就虐待緊佢哋"},{"pid":"bd9598b610e95da9605c61099230d22021f9f122","tid":481390,"uid":34915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T12:14:06.000Z","msg":"之前返過貓cafe,唔知幫你唔到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd6d23fdffb8c6fcbdfd6cbc52a25de6f2165661","tid":481390,"uid":73730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T14:27:59.000Z","msg":"養開寵物既人都會覺得動物cafe好on9"},{"pid":"834eeb2ecb4bca0ec92fd8914969932af59e6027","tid":481390,"uid":34915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T15:57:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>養開寵物既人都會覺得動物cafe好on9</blockquote><br />\n我本身屋企有狗，屋企唔俾我養貓，所以我去左貓cafe做<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n返過幾間，第一間都好dd 起碼我走之前d貓貓都仲有人理，果陣每晚都一定會幫佢地清潔下 抹下，依家點我就唔知，第二間我覺得d貓都幾慘 d貓貓成日有眼水 懷疑佢地有耳仔發炎，老細又西<br />\n<br />\n其實老老實實一間cafe放咁多貓，又要照顧貓 又要招呼客，做得邊樣啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再講每日有咁多唔同既客黎，好難避免有人亂餵佢地/唔知對佢地做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />試過有人過份到放蛋糕係地下俾貓食，好彩貓貓無事炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好啦，最後如果間cafe頂唔住，咁d貓點？俾人？定自己養？ <br />\n其實貓cafe d貓貓真係幾慘下，俾人當工具咁，仲聽過有老闆覺得貓貓唔得意唔痴人/有病要長醫就唔想要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99b0e86d79d04b0472b442ac94b8860f71a6e505","tid":481390,"uid":25321,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T15:59:42.000Z","msg":"啲貓日日比人煩比人摸唔比佢地瞓<br />\n慘過做雞"},{"pid":"3549e5ba55fb0b7d33fa04d2607767cf37414581","tid":481390,"uid":151540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T16:49:56.000Z","msg":"個target segment 咁細？<br />\n比較想知咩功課黎"}]}